Dataset Settings

train_data_dir

Training Dataset Path

reg_data_dir

Regularization Dataset Path. Default is empty, no use of regularized images

prior_loss_weight

Regularization - Prior Loss Weight

resolution

Training Image Resolution, Width x Height. Supports non-square, but must be a multiple of 64.

enable_bucket

Enable arb buckets to allow images with non-fixed aspect ratios

min_bucket_reso

Minimum Resolution for arb Buckets

max_bucket_reso

Maximum Resolution for arb Buckets

bucket_reso_steps

arb 桶分辨率划分单位，SDXL 可以使用 32

Learning Rate and Optimizer Settings

Network Settings

最小信噪比伽马值，如果启用推荐为 5

network_module

Train Network Module

Continue Training from Existing LoRA Model, Fill in Path

network_dim

Network Dimension, commonly used between 4 and 128, bigger isn't always better

Commonly the same as network_dim or a smaller value, like half of network_dim to prevent underflow. Using smaller alpha requires increasing the learning rate.

network_dropout

Dropout Probability (Incompatible with Lycoris, use built-in Lycoris)

scale_weight_norms

network_args_custom

Custom network_args, one per line

enable_block_weights

Enable Layer-wise Learning Rate Training (only for use in networks.lora, not compatible with other network modules)

enable_base_weight

最大范数正则化。如果使用，推荐为 1

Differential Alchemy

Training Preview Image Settings

Log Settings

log_with

Log Module

log_prefix

Log Prefix

log_tracker_name

Log Tracker Name

logging_dir

Logging Save Folder

caption_extension

Tag File Extension

shuffle_caption

Shuffle Tokens during Training

weighted_captions

Use Weighted Tokens, not recommended to enable with shuffle_caption

keep_tokens

Keep First N Tokens unchanged while shuffling

max_token_length

Maximum Token Length

caption_dropout_rate

Probability to Drop All Labels, no caption or class token for an image

caption_dropout_every_n_epochs

Drop All Labels every N epochs

caption_tag_dropout_rate

Probability to Randomly Drop Tags separated by commas

Noise Settings

noise_offset

multires_noise_iterations

Multi-resolution (Pyramid) Noise Iterations, recommended 6-10. Cannot be enabled with noise_offset

multires_noise_discount

Multi-resolution (Pyramid) Noise Discount, recommended 0.3-0.8, must be enabled with the above parameter multires_noise_iterations

Advanced Settings

seed

Random Seed

在训练中添加噪声偏移来改良生成非常暗或者非常亮的图像，如果启用推荐为 0.1

clip_skip

CLIP Skip Layers

Esoteric

Speed Optimization Options

mixed_precision

Train in Mixed Precision

full_fp16

Use Full FP16 Precision

full_bf16Use Full BF16 Precision

xformers

Enable Xformers

lowram

cache_latents

Cache Image Latent

cache_latents_to_disk

Cache Image Latent to Disk

cache_text_encoder_outputs

Cache Text Encoder Outputs, reduce VRAM usage. Requires shuffle_caption to be disabled.

cache_text_encoder_outputs_to_disk

Cache Text Encoder Outputs to Disk

persistent_data_loader_workers

Keep workers loading training set, reduce pauses between epochs.
